data.description: Perfect Gem in the Prestigious Neighborhood of Deer Trails. Great Oversized CulDeSac Lot w/Endless Possibilities for the family looking for a 4Bed/2Bath home that loves to entertain! This home is a split floorplan w/inviting entryway, hardwood floors, spacious formal dining & family room. Open kitchen w/tons of cabinets and granite countertops. The Primary Suite has ample space to house oversize furniture plus Hollywood-style bathroom with w/separate vanities, soaking tub/tall walk-in shower, and closets. Nice size secondary bedrooms & utility room. Spacious backyard with covered patio for those Hot Texas Summers.  Low tax rate, low HOA, and no MUD minutes from I-45, Conroe and The Woodlands, come and view today!
